{"tid":28330,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人收集緊日本100名城","createTime":"2016-12-08T01:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T13:22:13.000Z","uid":59953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"898cfe9f14786e05c1ba185005a09823550f053c","tid":28330,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:06:15.000Z","msg":"大家收到第幾個"},{"pid":"f4be0b64226b8857d842e2f22a17bd738ac04be7","tid":28330,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:09:18.000Z","msg":"早幾日去日本收左2個<br />\n有部分可能要掉低老婆自己去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546c8dfd48d3aec415820fbd8e8a9ac56435cd26","tid":28330,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊一次過去哂九州既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13d7ef4d3e66b4b9850740160668d76e150ad973","tid":28330,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:32:59.000Z","msg":"有去行城, 但冇收集印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時去過犬山城, 名古屋城, 彥根城, 大阪城, 姬路城, 岡山城, 廣島城, 熊本城, 備中松山城, 松山城, 丸龜城, 宇和島城"},{"pid":"e1a26184e63b267f385fecd95d8541c4121bb77d","tid":28330,"uid":47041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"犬山城 名古屋城 大阪城 二條城<br />\n四個<br />\n黎馬諗住去松江城同廣島城"},{"pid":"9f43d21280eef8d87c90d9eb7986ca15ed2c6a87","tid":28330,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:03:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早幾日去日本收左2個<br />\n有部分可能要掉低老婆自己去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行山城帶老婆去隨時客死異鄉"},{"pid":"f180e1dc900a058f2eadf9874895079f3bf2ce72","tid":28330,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊一次過去哂九州既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n島原城 平戶城遠到仆街"},{"pid":"7affd28442c32389d30e820f19b5cb1127342e33","tid":28330,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊一次過去哂九州既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n島原城 平戶城遠到仆街</blockquote><br />\n揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> no fear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b4bf5a3c1d7e6fccb6b3fab02bb1d2675e5bf5","tid":28330,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:11:39.000Z","msg":"因為有次夏天行山城差d中暑死，所以決定左遠既城一定會揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de897c31eeb01b2bdf0f467ca70e6a6ad0b74cd","tid":28330,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為有次夏天行山城差d中暑死，所以決定左遠既城一定會揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行邊個城咁"},{"pid":"0410e10b777b1f477044241503de9c8b93a25d82","tid":28330,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為有次夏天行山城差d中暑死，所以決定左遠既城一定會揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行邊個城咁</blockquote><br />\n金山城，一來果日太曬，二來前一日休息得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://miraigajettokenkyujo.blogspot.com/2016/10/201609-day-1_2.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmiraigajettokenkyujo.blogspot.com%2F2016%2F10%2F201609-day-1_2.html%3Fm%3D1&d=7Q37PLU0iRpdUxo743K20EsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=56bcc2e4\" target=\"_blank\">http://miraigajettokenkyujo.blogspot.com/2016/10/201609-day-1_2.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"626880b832f9ceb1b9f83f519c55fa6a19399786","tid":28330,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:38:49.000Z","msg":"想儲現存天守<em></em>"},{"pid":"47802005c990db39083809e31292006d9112ffdf","tid":28330,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"100就唔會，但係12現存天守就收集緊"},{"pid":"fbe8ff72b6156218b95bb4841a01f814dd94ee50","tid":28330,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>100就唔會，但係12現存天守就收集緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現存去過7個了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n姬路城、備中松山城、丸龜城、松山城、宇和島城、彥根城、犬山城<br />\n<br />\n下年會去埋松本城同高知城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1271c73f5eec94b2100bf7ad9699b20eb53bc109","tid":28330,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>100就唔會，但係12現存天守就收集緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現存去過7個了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n姬路城、備中松山城、丸龜城、松山城、宇和島城、彥根城、犬山城<br />\n<br />\n下年會去埋松本城同高知城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你四國去剩高知城下次要特登去個度好似好唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3943a12ee9156c9e329594bb0441811a86661942","tid":28330,"uid":38895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:58:13.000Z","msg":"熊本城而家有得捐1萬yen做一口城主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f569babca8de31c1587fb60749d52f191ee4a64","tid":28330,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>100就唔會，但係12現存天守就收集緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現存去過7個了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n姬路城、備中松山城、丸龜城、松山城、宇和島城、彥根城、犬山城<br />\n<br />\n下年會去埋松本城同高知城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你四國去剩高知城下次要特登去個度好似好唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上次玩北部，今次玩南部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去得3日好難一次跑晒4個城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b2bdf0b5fde5179a130bd2baff34df04713695","tid":28330,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"行過幾個冇留印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996d294138b1af9534b1786b8ddd7414ed7233e8","tid":28330,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T04:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行過幾個冇留印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去人吉城果時未買本書仔,淨係搵張紙仔cup個印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b348024a26bba29cc00cae9084b177b3f01bd28","tid":28330,"uid":13199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"剩係去過松山城同丸龜城。去完就想去曬十二現存天守。下個月諗住去姬路城。"},{"pid":"184857db327f4891d2c94c297508177bab1744ac","tid":28330,"uid":51061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T21:48:47.000Z","msg":"剛剛起步<br />\n印象中4個<br />\n大阪姫路明石江戶<br />\n下次繼續"},{"pid":"c31f7a40c3f017db5c3c9c5f548b274fb7ce5235","tid":28330,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:42:54.000Z","msg":"4個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034f14f898958ec04184ae1b7b2028527e863aa1","tid":28330,"uid":56775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:54:55.000Z","msg":"行大坂城掉低左女朋友自己係觀景台三個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己慢慢睇真係好爽"},{"pid":"a1b354cbc16c48ae15aaae58fc1624fd97e3c874","tid":28330,"uid":20258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>100就唔會，但係12現存天守就收集緊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現存去過7個了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n姬路城、備中松山城、丸龜城、松山城、宇和島城、彥根城、犬山城<br />\n<br />\n下年會去埋松本城同高知城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你四國去剩高知城下次要特登去個度好似好唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n四國反而係我最想再去既地方"},{"pid":"c3588d4994e3fb4b66b29bf95b857140e457cd4d","tid":28330,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行大坂城掉低左女朋友自己係觀景台三個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己慢慢睇真係好爽</blockquote><br />\n有冇跪玻璃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW 我覺得重建既城都好, 好似大阪城/熊本城咁有展望台好過名古屋城咁上到頂都係記念品鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e267e13b9a06244e61f5476fe0d9f1a7230cfff2","tid":28330,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:34:07.000Z","msg":"下星期去日本睇波順便收集多幾個印<br />\n希望到時儲到第50個"},{"pid":"fe8733a22ac8ba7e0e66b3f767d6ed48a7db1aa1","tid":28330,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:27:04.000Z","msg":"收集左差唔多廿幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n福岡城、島原城、佐賀城、吉野ヶ里、飫肥城、鹿兒島城、熊本城、人吉城、廣島城、備中松山城、岩國城、岡山城、姬路城、丸龜城、高松城、大阪城、二條城、彥根城、岐阜城、名古屋城、伊賀上野城、岡崎城、犬山城、松本城、高岡城<br />\n另外去左唔入百名城名單嘅有小倉城、清洲城、大垣城、富山城"},{"pid":"70465bf25af34df2d34b0e6c9dbbf5ee8d47d129","tid":28330,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊一次過去哂九州既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n島原城 平戶城遠到仆街</blockquote><br />\n揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> no fear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n島原基本上一定要住一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐵膠可以搭島鐵"},{"pid":"796523c247dc2cc18b83293666358f3b416f6dee","tid":28330,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T15:32:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收集左差唔多廿幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n福岡城、島原城、佐賀城、吉野ヶ里、飫肥城、鹿兒島城、熊本城、人吉城、廣島城、備中松山城、岩國城、岡山城、姬路城、丸龜城、高松城、大阪城、二條城、彥根城、岐阜城、名古屋城、伊賀上野城、岡崎城、犬山城、松本城、高岡城<br />\n另外去左唔入百名城名單嘅有小倉城、清洲城、大垣城、富山城</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n漏左個位於諫早嘅高城城"},{"pid":"0bc5b89ee56e31c94790bd7b7c3e04bcc378a5f9","tid":28330,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T22:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊一次過去哂九州既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n島原城 平戶城遠到仆街</blockquote><br />\n揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> no fear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n島原基本上一定要住一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐵膠可以搭島鐵</blockquote><br />\n我上次一早去睇得一個鐘再趕返去軍艦島"},{"pid":"9c224688d9c71efc38104397aedbdc3ea0f7065b","tid":28330,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>25<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊一次過去哂九州既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n島原城 平戶城遠到仆街</blockquote><br />\n揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> no fear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n島原基本上一定要住一晚<img src=\"/ass