te><br />\n見到遊記就唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18add0536054b763641e168273e2388744513ab1","tid":28330,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T14:23:14.000Z","msg":"聽日去名護屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991cf10fbd26527664477e90c62bc40d76a37fdd","tid":28330,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T22:48:58.000Z","msg":"今朝新聞播陸自去左島原城個石垣清雜草<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0109b0149aed01a5bcde45f3ae2a41d4d8235c9","tid":28330,"uid":59953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"今日去左二本松城<br />\n聽日去白河"},{"pid":"923f2f8d9e7d4799f88af0c9c0c3864a6940b450","tid":28330,"uid":33566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T02:20:33.000Z","msg":"岩岩去完佐賀城 (其實得個御殿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但講維新時期既資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整蒸氣火車，蒸氣船，反射爐煉鐵整鑄大炮，長崎設台場做港口防衛，三重津海軍學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個九州既人係果段時期都跑得好前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當江戶人都係柒下柒下既時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween一陣諗住去吉野里公園但出面倒緊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係佐賀駅間Mister Donut坐緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3bad0868268ffacabaa8b0dff92989fbc045ffa","tid":28330,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:18:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩去完佐賀城 (其實得個御殿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但講維新時期既資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整蒸氣火車，蒸氣船，反射爐煉鐵整鑄大炮，長崎設台場做港口防衛，三重津海軍學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm